▪️ Dollar value of the ETH pool (Teth) = ETHpool * Veth

▪️ Dollar value of the CORE pool (Tcore) = COREpool * Vcore

▪️# of CORE for trading (TRADEcore) = COREsupply – COREpool

▪️ # of ETH obtained by selling all TRADEcore for ETH (COREout) = Check this one on Uniswap manually.  Anyone got a better method?

▪️ # of ETH remaining in pool after COREout is removed (Weth) = ETHpool – COREout

▪️ Total CORE supply (COREsupply) – 10,000 (cannot be changed)
▪️ # of CORE in the liquidity pool (COREpool) 
▪️ # of ETH in the liquidity pool (ETHpool) 
▪️ LP Token Value (LPV) 
▪️ Total LP Supply (TLPmax) 
▪️ Current USD value of ETH (Veth)
▪️ Current USD value of CORE (Vcore)
